definitions.definition: ( of a woman ) Homosexual , gay ; preferring exclusively women as romantic or sexual partners .
examples: Lesbian fans of the show were rooting for Jane and Amanda to get together.

subdefinitions.definition: ( of a woman , loosely ) Preferring primarily women as romantic or sexual partners .

definitions.definition: ( of a romantic or sexual act or relationship ) Between two or more women; homosexual , gay .
( especially of an institution or group ) Intended for lesbians .
examples: We're going to a lesbian bar tonight.

definitions.definition: ( now rare ) Alternative letter-case form of Lesbian ( “ of or pertaining to the island of Lesbos ” ) .
